        <mxCell id="e1"
          value="① Orchestrator.run()&lt;br&gt;&lt;small&gt;detect multi-step pattern: /\bthen\b|\balso\b|\bfirst\b|\beach\b/i&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;simple mode&lt;/b&gt;: run ReActLoop once&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;multi-step mode&lt;/b&gt;: LLM decompose() → JSON sub-task array → ReActLoop × N&lt;br&gt;global token budget: 100,000 tokens&lt;/small&gt;"
          style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;fontSize=10;"
          vertex="1" parent="edit_c">
          <mxGeometry x="20" y="40" width="690" height="84" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <mxCell id="e2"
          value="② ReActLoop  (max 10 steps · abort after 3 consecutive tool errors)&lt;br&gt;&lt;small&gt;&lt;b&gt;[THOUGHT]&lt;/b&gt; reasoning...&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;[ACTION {&quot;tool&quot;: &quot;file_scan&quot; | &quot;file_read&quot; | &quot;r_exec&quot;,  &quot;input&quot;: { ... }}]&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;→ ToolRegistry.execute()  →  append  &lt;b&gt;[OBSERVATION]&lt;/b&gt;  to messages  →  next step&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;[ANSWER]&lt;/b&gt; final response: JSON [{path, content}, ...]  or  plain text&lt;/small&gt;"
          style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;fontSize=10;"
          vertex="1" parent="edit_c">
